<!--
Load the Mermaid library, which renders the diagrams written in ```mermaid code
blocks (the mdbook-mermaid preprocessor transforms these blocks into
<pre class="mermaid"> elements; this library then renders them client-side).

We load the library from a CDN instead of vendoring the ~2.5 MB minified file
in the repository. The version is pinned and the integrity hash ensures the
browser rejects the script if the CDN ever serves different bytes. Keep the
version in sync with the one bundled by mdbook-mermaid (11.6.0 as of
mdbook-mermaid 0.17.0), which is what `book/mermaid-init.js` is written
against.
-->
<script
  src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mermaid@11.6.0/dist/mermaid.min.js"
  integrity="sha384-zkWMJO4sgpPUzyuOgDx8HB/K55glbAwajEpk1Go2NWRuPkPA/wIhoEJTuSkmOYrV"
  crossorigin="anonymous"
></script>
